{
"#name"
:
{
"dbnomics"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"DBnomics 经济数据 API 客户端"
,
"en"
:
"DBnomics economic data API client"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x dbnomics <subcmd> [options] [args]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x dbnomics data <alias|series_id>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x dbnomics align [--csv|--tsv] <id1> <id2> <id3>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"DBnomics 是全球最大的经济数据聚合平台之一，涵盖 IMF、世界银行、欧洲央行等机构的免费数据。\n本模块是 x-cmd 对 DBnomics Web API (v22) 的轻量级 CLI 封装。\n"
,
"en"
:
"DBnomics is one of the world's largest economic data aggregators, covering free data from IMF, World Bank, ECB, and more.\nThis module is x-cmd's lightweight CLI wrapper for the DBnomics Web API (v22).\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"无需认证即可使用，所有 API 请求通过 x ccmd 缓存 1 小时。\n文档: https://api.db.nomics.world/v22\n"
,
"en"
:
"No authentication required. All API requests are cached for 1 hour via x ccmd.\nDocs: https://api.db.nomics.world/v22\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"探索数据的推荐路径：\n1. x dbnomics alias — 查看预置别名（us.cpi、bis.eur 等）\n2. x dbnomics search <关键词> — 全文搜索数据集\n3. x dbnomics provider — 浏览数据提供者\n4. x dbnomics dataset <provider> — 浏览具体数据集\n5. x dbnomics series <provider> <dataset> — 列出序列\n"
,
"en"
:
"Recommended exploration path:\n1. x dbnomics alias — check pre-defined aliases (us.cpi, bis.eur, etc.)\n2. x dbnomics search <keyword> — full-text search datasets\n3. x dbnomics provider — browse data providers\n4. x dbnomics dataset <provider> — browse specific datasets\n5. x dbnomics series <provider> <dataset> — list series\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"查找完整序列 ID 的路径:\n1. x dbnomics provider — 找到 provider_code（如 IMF、BIS）\n2. x dbnomics dataset <provider> — 找到 dataset_code（如 WEO:2024-10）\n3. x dbnomics series <provider> <dataset> — 找到 series_code\n完整 ID 格式: provider_code/dataset_code/series_code\n"
,
"en"
:
"How to find a full series ID:\n1. x dbnomics provider — find provider_code (e.g. IMF, BIS)\n2. x dbnomics dataset <provider> — find dataset_code (e.g. WEO:2024-10)\n3. x dbnomics series <provider> <dataset> — find series_code\nFull ID format: provider_code/dataset_code/series_code\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"data 子命令只支持单序列。多序列对齐请用 align 子命令。\n"
,
"en"
:
"The data subcommand only supports single series. Use align for multi-series aligned output.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"IMF WEO 数据单位说明：persons 为百万人、us_dollars 为十亿美元、pcent_change 为百分比变化。\nDBnomics API 不提供量级信息，具体量级以各数据源官方文档为准。\n"
,
"en"
:
"IMF WEO unit notes: persons = millions, us_dollars = billions, pcent_change = percent change.\nDBnomics API does not provide magnitude info; refer to each data source's official docs.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"IMF WEO 动态别名 — imf.<国家代码>.<指标后缀>\n示例: imf.th.gdp（泰国GDP）、imf.kr.cpi（韩国CPI）、imf.cn.gdp.growth（中国GDP增长率）\n查询国家代码: x dbnomics code region2\n查询指标后缀: x dbnomics code weoseries\n"
,
"en"
:
"IMF WEO dynamic alias — imf.<cc>.<suffix>\nExamples: imf.th.gdp (Thailand GDP), imf.kr.cpi (Korea CPI), imf.cn.gdp.growth (China GDP growth)\nCountry codes: x dbnomics code region2\nIndicator suffixes: x dbnomics code weoseries\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"IMF WEO 经济联盟别名 — imf.<联盟代码>.<指标后缀>\n示例: imf.eu.gdp（欧盟GDP）、imf.g7.gdp.growth（G7增长率）、imf.asean.ppp（东盟PPP）\n联盟代码: eu(欧盟)、euro(欧元区)、g7、asean、world、advanced、emerging、latam、mideast、devasia、africa、deveur\n查询完整列表: x dbnomics code weoagg\n"
,
"en"
:
"IMF WEO economic group alias — imf.<group>.<suffix>\nExamples: imf.eu.gdp (EU GDP), imf.g7.gdp.growth (G7 growth), imf.asean.ppp (ASEAN PPP)\nGroups: eu (EU), euro (Euro area), g7, asean, world, advanced, emerging, latam, mideast, devasia, africa, deveur\nFull list: x dbnomics code weoagg\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"BIS 汇率动态别名 — bis.<货币代码>（月度兑 USD 汇率）\n示例: bis.eur（欧元）、bis.cny（人民币）、bis.jpy（日元）\n查询货币代码: x dbnomics code currency\n"
,
"en"
:
"BIS exchange rate dynamic alias — bis.<currency> (monthly vs USD)\nExamples: bis.eur (Euro), bis.cny (CNY), bis.jpy (JPY)\nCurrency codes: x dbnomics code currency\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"BIS 央行利率动态别名 — bis.rate.<国家代码>（月度政策利率）\n示例: bis.rate.us（美联储）、bis.rate.eu（ECB）、bis.rate.jp（日本央行）\n查询国家代码: x dbnomics code cbpol\n"
,
"en"
:
"BIS central bank rate dynamic alias — bis.rate.<cc> (monthly policy rate)\nExamples: bis.rate.us (Fed), bis.rate.eu (ECB), bis.rate.jp (BOJ)\nCountry codes: x dbnomics code cbpol\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"预置别名（bls.cpi、fed.10y、wb.gold 等）由 x dbnomics alias 管理。\n不含 / 的 ID 先匹配动态别名，再查预置 alias 表。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Pre-configured aliases (bls.cpi, fed.10y, wb.gold, etc.) managed by x dbnomics alias.\nIDs without / match dynamic patterns first, then pre-configured alias table.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"gov.* 指标区分绝对值与占比：gov.revenue 为本国货币总量，gov.revenue.gdp 为占 GDP%。\nppp.share 为该国占世界 GDP 的百分比（PPP 基础）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"gov.* indicators distinguish absolute vs ratio: gov.revenue is national currency, gov.revenue.gdp is % of GDP.\nppp.share is the country's share of world GDP (PPP basis).\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x dbnomics data imf.cn.gdp.growth"
,
"cn"
:
"获取中国 GDP 增长率（IMF WEO 年度）"
,
"en"
:
"Fetch China GDP growth rate (IMF WEO annual)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x dbnomics data imf.us.ppp"
,
"cn"
:
"获取美国 PPP GDP（购买力平价）"
,
"en"
:
