"data"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"直接获取单条时间序列的观测数据"
,
"en"
:
"Directly fetch observations for a single series"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"只支持单序列。多序列请用 align 子命令。"
,
"en"
:
"Only single series supported. Use align for multiple series."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"不带格式选项时，交互终端下以 csv app 浏览，管道或重定向则以 TSV 输出。"
,
"en"
:
"Without a format flag, interactive terminals open csv app; pipe or redirect outputs TSV."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"支持别名: 不含 / 的 ID 先匹配动态别名，再查预置 alias 表。详见 x dbnomics --help"
,
"en"
:
"Aliases: IDs without / match dynamic patterns first, then alias table. See x dbnomics --help"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x dbnomics data imf.cn.gdp.growth"
,
"cn"
:
"获取中国 GDP 增长率，交互终端以 csv app 浏览，管道则以 TSV 输出"
,
"en"
:
"Fetch China GDP growth rate; interactive terminal opens csv app, pipe outputs TSV"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x dbnomics data --csv imf.us.gdp"
,
"cn"
:
"CSV 格式: 美国GDP，适合数据库导入、表格软件或脚本处理"
,
"en"
:
"CSV format: US GDP, suitable for database import, spreadsheets, or scripting"
}
