"align"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"获取多条时间序列并对齐到统一时间轴"
,
"en"
:
"Fetch multiple series aligned to a unified time axis"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"不带格式选项时，交互终端下以 csv app 浏览，管道或重定向则以 TSV 输出。"
,
"en"
:
"Without a format flag, interactive terminals open csv app; pipe or redirect outputs TSV."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"内部使用 JSON API (align_periods=1) 实现真正对齐，缺失值填充 null。"
,
"en"
:
"Internally uses JSON API (align_periods=1) for true alignment, missing values filled with null."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"建议同 provider 同频率的序列一起对齐，避免大量 null。"
,
"en"
:
"Align series from the same provider with the same frequency to avoid excessive nulls."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"别名和完整 ID 的查找方式详见 x dbnomics --help"
,
"en"
:
"See x dbnomics --help for alias and full ID lookup methods"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x dbnomics align imf.us.cpi imf.de.cpi imf.jp.cpi"
,
"cn"
:
"对比美/德/日 CPI，交互终端以 csv app 浏览，管道则以 TSV 输出"
,
"en"
:
"Compare US/Germany/Japan CPI; interactive terminal opens csv app, pipe outputs TSV"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x dbnomics align --csv imf.us.gdp imf.cn.gdp"
,
"cn"
:
"CSV 格式: 对比美/中 GDP，适合数据库导入、表格软件或脚本处理"
,
"en"
:
"CSV format: Compare US/China GDP, suitable for database import, spreadsheets, or scripting"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x dbnomics align --tsv fed.10y fed.2y fed.3m"
,
"cn"
:
"TSV 格式: 对比美国国债收益率曲线，适合管道和 awk/grep 处理"
,
"en"
:
"TSV format: Compare US Treasury yield curve, suitable for piping with awk/grep"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x dbnomics align --json imf.us.cpi imf.cn.cpi imf.de.cpi"
,
"cn"
:
"JSON 格式: 对比美/中/德 CPI，返回完整 API 响应，适合程序处理"
,
"en"
:
"JSON format: Compare US/China/Germany CPI, full API response for programmatic use"
}
